Farmers use a cart to haul a load of wheat during a harvest in the village of Fatehganj in Punjab province, Pakistan, on May 3. Pakistan is Asia's third-largest grower of wheat. Visit  www.bloomberg.com/sustainability  for the latest from Bloomberg News about energy, natural resources and global business.